OL,3,CMan and woman named after alleged
OL,4,C'racially motivated incident' by mosque
OL,6,FThe States of Jersey Police have
OL,7,Freleased more information following
OL,8,Fwhat they are calling a "racially
OL,9,Fmotivated incident" outside the
OL,10,Fisland's Islamic Centre.
OL,12,FAn altercation took place on Aquila
OL,13,FRoad in St Helier, outside the mosque,
OL,14,Fat approximately 2pm on Friday 6 March.
OL,16,FTwo people were arrested following the
OL,17,Fincident, which happened during the
OL,18,FIslamic holy month of Ramadan.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
