OL,3,CMan and woman named after alleged
OL,4,C'racially motivated incident' by mosque
OL,6,FPolice continue to appeal to anyone
OL,7,Fwho may have witnessed the incident or
OL,8,Fhas information that could assist the
OL,9,Finvestigation to contact them on 01534
OL,10,F612612 or Crimestoppers anonymously on
OL,11,F0800 555 111.
OL,13,FJersey Police's Community Safety Team
OL,14,Fsays it is supporting members of the
OL,15,FMuslim community, with patrols in the
OL,16,Farea for the rest of Ramadan, which
OL,17,Fends on Thursday 19 March.
